'''Baak-gaa-seng''' ([[百家姓]]) heh ngit phun gwaan-yi Zung-wun seng-si geh [[si]]. Gaai si heung Bak-sung tsoh nen chok-saa. Yen sau zaap 411 goh seng-si, hau-lui zang-ga du 504 goh. Seng-si ngit gung nip-men yu 444 goh daan seng thung 60 goh fuk seng. Baak-gaa-seng geh tsi-zui ng heh gok seng-si ngin-hau sak-zai phaai-lit, heh yan-wai thuk laai sun-hau, yi hok haau gi.

[[Saam-zi-gang]], Baak-gaa-seng tung [[Tsen-zi-wun]] hap tsang "Saam baak tsen". Heung yu Hon-zi wun-fa geh gok-gaa haau  chung-yew.

